    "name": "Arcane Denial counters a spell, controller draws",
    "description": "p1 casts Harmonize (sorcery). p2 casts Arcane Denial targeting Harmonize. Arcane Denial resolves: Harmonize is countered, its controller (p1) draws 2 next upkeep, and p2 draws a card immediately. Tests that Arcane Denial produces the full effect sequence: counter target spell, controller draws 2 at beginning of their next upkeep (trigger), caster draws 1 now.",
